Interface FileStoreTable

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DataTable, InnerTable, Serializable, Table
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DelegatedFileStoreTable, FallbackReadFileStoreTable, PrivilegedFileStoreTable

    public interface FileStoreTable
extends DataTable
    An abstraction layer above FileStore to provide reading and writing of InternalRow.
